FBIS4-60862 "drsov084_r_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 Azerbaijan New Interior Minister Ramil Usubov Profiled New Interior Minister Ramil Usubov Profiled NC2904203394 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network in Azeri 1600 GMT 29 Apr 94 NC2904203394 Baku Azerbaycan Radio Televiziyasi Television Network Azeri BFN [Text] Here is a short profile of the new interior minister appointed by presidential decree. Ramil Idris ogly Usubov was born in Khodzhaly in 1948. Since the 1970's he has been working in the police organs. He was the interior minister of Nakhichevan Autonomous Republic [NAR] in the years 1987-89. He served as the head of the passports and visa department and then as the head of a desk in the personnel department at the Interior Ministry until June 1993. He has been working again as the interior minister of NAR since June 1993. He is a lawyer by profession, and a graduate of the police academy. He is married and has three children.
